descriptionNullable:
Original source: https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/mylesoneill/tagged-anime-illustrations

This dataset takes images and tags from the original source and processes them such that images (.jpgs) and captions (.txts) are in the same folder. This makes it easier to train models like imagen (i.e. using deepglug/imagen's script).
